Document: OggPacketSequence
Path: godot/classes/class_oggpacketsequence.rst
Summary: Properties and their default values for the OggPacketSequence class

Property: granule_positions (PackedInt64Array): Stores granule position data for packets. Default: PackedInt64Array()
Property: packet_data (Array of Arrays): Contains the raw packet data as nested arrays. Default: []
Property: sampling_rate (float): Specifies the audio sampling rate in Hz. Default: 0.0
