Document: OggPacketSequence  
Path: godot/classes/class_oggpacketsequence.rst  
Summary: Describes the granule_positions, packet_data, and sampling_rate properties of the OggPacketSequence class.  

PackedInt64Array granule_positions = PackedInt64Array()  
Set/Get: void set_packet_granule_positions(value: PackedInt64Array)  
PackedInt64Array get_packet_granule_positions()  
Contains the granule positions for each page in this packet sequence. Note: The returned array is copied and any changes to it will not update the original property value.  

Array<Array> packet_data = []  
Set/Get: void set_packet_data(value: Array<Array>)  
Array<Array> get_packet_data()  
Contains the raw packets that make up this OggPacketSequence.  

float sampling_rate = 0.0  
Set/Get: void set_sampling_rate(value: float)  
float get_sampling_rate()  
Holds sample rate information about this sequence. Note: Must be set by another class that actually understands the codec.
---CHUNK---
